trans-unit.source: The TANH function returns the hyperbolic tangent of a specified number.

seg-source.mrk: The TANH function returns the hyperbolic tangent of a specified number.

target.mrk: The TANH function returns the hyperbolic tangent of a specified number.

trans-unit.source: The specified number is the angle, in radians, that you want the hyperbolic tangent for. The specified number must be a <xref href="rrefsqljdoubleprecision.dita#rrefsqljdoubleprecision">DOUBLE PRECISION</xref> number.

trans-unit.source: If the specified number is NULL, the result of this function is NULL.
